---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Sidebar from '../components/Sidebar.astro';
import Section from '../components/Section.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import PageNav from '../components/PageNav.astro';
import { sections } from '../data/sections';

const idx = 0;
---

<Layout title="Git — Estructura de Ramas">
  <Sidebar slot="sidebar" />
  <div class="container">
    <Section title="Estructura de Ramas" id="estructura-de-ramas">
      <p>El repositorio tiene hasta <strong>tres ramas permanentes</strong>. Todas las demás son temporales y se eliminan al fusionarse.</p>
      <div class="flow">
        <div class="flow-row">
          <span class="branch-badge b-feature">feat/456-login-google</span>
          <span class="arrow">→</span>
          <span class="branch-badge b-main">main</span>
          <span style="font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);margin-left:8px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;">← MR formal</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flow-row">
          <span class="branch-badge b-feature">feat/456-login-google</span>
          <span class="arrow">→</span>
          <span class="branch-badge b-testing">testing</span>
          <span style="font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);margin-left:8px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;">← merge directo</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flow-row">
          <span class="branch-badge b-feature">feat/456-login-google</span>
          <span class="arrow">→</span>
          <span class="branch-badge b-next">next / stage</span>
          <span style="font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);margin-left:8px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;">← condicional</span>
        </div>

        <div class="flow-legend">
          <div class="flow-row"><span class="branch-badge b-main">main</span><span class="flow-desc">Producción. Solo código aprobado vía MR formal.</span></div>
          <div class="flow-row"><span class="branch-badge b-testing">testing</span><span class="flow-desc">QA e integración. Permite push/merge directo por developers.</span></div>
          <div class="flow-row"><span class="branch-badge b-next" style="background:var(--accent3)">next / stage</span><span class="flow-desc">Pre-producción. Solo si el proyecto cuenta con instancia stage.</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h3>Protección por rama</h3>
      <div class="table-wrapper">
        <table>
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th>Configuración</th>
              <th><code>main</code></th>
              <th><code>testing</code></th>
              <th><code>stage</code></th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <td>Merge por</td>
              <td>Maintainers</td>
              <td>Developers</td>
              <td>Maintainers</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>Push directo</td>
              <td>Nadie</td>
              <td>Developers</td>
              <td>Maintainers</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>Approval MR</td>
              <td>Sí (mín. 1)</td>
              <td>N/A</td>
              <td>N/A</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <h3>Reset periódico de <code>testing</code></h3>
      <p><code>testing</code> puede acumular estado corrupto. Se recomienda resetearlo periódicamente (force-push de <code>main</code> a <code>testing</code>) solo por el Team Leader.</p>
      <pre><code><span class="cm"># Reset de testing desde main (solo Team Leader)</span>
git checkout main
git pull origin main
git push origin main:testing --force</code></pre>

      <div class="alert"><strong>Regla de oro:</strong> Nunca push directo a <code>main</code>. <code>testing</code> permite push directo por developers para agilizar procesos de integración y QA.</div>
    </Section>
    <PageNav prev={sections[idx - 1] ?? null} next={sections[idx + 1] ?? null} />
    <Footer />
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .flow-legend {
    margin-top: 24px;
    display: grid;
    gap: 12px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding-top: 24px;
  }
  .b-next { background: var(--accent3); color: #000; }
  .flow-legend .flow-row { margin-bottom: 0; align-items: flex-start; }
  .flow-desc { font-size: 14px; margin-top: 4px; }
</style>
